比莉·艾利什表演时被粉丝扔出的项链击中https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-hit-by-necklace- thrown-by-fan-while-performing-3822272?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billie-eilish-hit-by-表演时项链被粉丝扔出Emma WilkesSat, 14 Dec 2024 20:51:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3822272 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾利什此前曾表示，这种事以前发生在她身上，并称其“令人愤怒”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-hit-by-necklace-thrown-by-fan-while-performing-3822272">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 在表演时被粉丝扔出的项链击中的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="比莉·艾利什" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/billie-eilishparas-griffin-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比莉·艾利什</a>在表演时被粉丝扔到舞台上的项链击中脸部。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/billie-eilish-hit-me-hard-and-soft-review-tracklist-lyrics-3756826">Billie Eilish – 《Hit Me Hard And Soft》评论：大胆、精彩、更明亮</a></strong></li></ul><p>艾利什昨晚（12 月 13 日）在亚利桑那州的沙漠钻石竞技场进行了一场演出，盘腿坐在地板上唱着“What Was I Made For？”事件发生时。</p><p>粉丝拍摄的视频显示，当项链击中艾莉什时，她瑟瑟发抖，人群惊讶地反应，还发出一些嘘声。艾利什迅速继续唱歌，然后拿起项链扔到一边。</p><p>该艺术家尚未对此事发表评论。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 在今晚的音乐会上被人群扔下的一条项链击中。</p><p> <a href="https://t.co/OQUg8i4rSy">pic.twitter.com/OQUg8i4rSy</a></p><p> - Buzzing Pop (@BuzzingPop) <a href="https://twitter.com/BuzzingPop/status/1867839522341335355?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 14 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>去年，多位艺人在舞台上被 <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/crowd-throwing-fans-musicians-injury-3465598">粉丝投掷物品</a>，引发娱乐圈广泛关注。艾利什本人表示， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">这种趋势“令人愤怒”。</a></p><p> “人们只是变得兴奋，这可能很危险，”她说，试图解释为什么她认为一些粉丝向艺术家扔东西。 “我对此有复杂的感觉，因为当你站在上面时，它会爆炸。但你知道这是出于爱，他们只是想给你一些东西。”</p><p> “我们明白了，但不要这样做，”她补充道。 “当你在上面的时候，这绝对令人愤怒。你处于弱势地位。”</p><p> “六年来，我一直在舞台上受到各种打击。我不知道为什么这是新的，”她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>世界首映式上告诉<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/music-news/billie-eilish-finneas-fans-throwing-objects-artists-onstage-1235531852/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞报道</em></a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园</a>演唱会上，一名<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pink-stunned-as-fan-throws-mothers-ashes-onto-stage-at-bst-hyde-park-3461977">歌迷将一袋她母亲的骨灰扔到舞台上，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">平克</a>感到震惊。在另一场演出中，一位粉丝<a href="https://www.huffpost.com/entry/pink-cheese-london_n_649d9ce1e4b0035bc5c526c2">从前排</a>递给<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">P!nk</a>一整轮奶酪。</p><p>此后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-nas-x">Lil Nas X</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lil-nas-x-pauses-gig-after-fan-throws-sex-toy-on-stage-3464509">短暂停止了在斯德哥尔摩的一场演出，以应对人造性玩具意外出现在舞台上的情况</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bebe-rexha-reveals-facial-injuries-after-having-phone-thrown-at-her-attacker-arrested-3458053">Bebe Rexha 在纽约一场演出中被手机击中脸部后需要缝针</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steve-lacy-smashes-fans-phone-and-storms-offstage-during-new-orleans-concert-3335765">史蒂夫·莱西还砸碎了扔给他的手机</a>。</p><p>许多其他艺术家也呼吁音乐会观众停止在舞台上扔东西，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adele-calls-on-fans-to-stop-throwing-things-at-artists-on-stage-3464740">阿黛尔</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kelly-clarkson-warns-fans-against-throwing-things-onstage-at-las-vegas-residency-3476190">凯莉·克拉克森</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/latto-says-someone-will-get-their-ass-beat-if-a-fan-threw-something-at-her-again-3469364-3469364">拉托</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-fans-throwing-objects-at-performers-is-infuriating-3468291">将这种趋势描述为“令人愤怒”</a> ，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Slipknot</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists-corey-taylor">Corey Taylor</a>则表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/corey-taylor-on-fans-throwing-things-at-performers-artists-arent-regarded-as-people-anymore-3479191">“艺术家不再被视为人”</a> 。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-urges-fans-to-not-throw-things-on-stage-it-really-freaks-me-out-3537390">告诉歌迷不要在舞台上向她扔东西</a>，坚称这“真的让我感到害怕”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="比莉·艾利什：小桌子音乐会" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fOAIrUZbOwo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>其他新闻方面，Eilish 最近在她的兄弟<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Finneas">Finneas</a>的陪同下，自 2020 年以来首次在<em>NPR Tiny Desk</em>上表演。她演奏了四首原声曲目，告诉华盛顿的小观众，这对她来说是一个“令人紧张”的时刻。</p><p>她表演了《The Greatest》、《L&#39;Amour de Ma Vie》和《Birds Of A Feather》的精简版，后者最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024">被<i>NME</i>评为 2024 年最佳歌曲第 12 名</a>。</p><p>这三首歌均取自《Hit Me Hard And Soft》，该歌曲也入围<em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-albums-2024-3818995">2024 年最佳专辑排行榜，排名第九</a>。但艾利什的深切让粉丝们感到惊讶，并演唱了她的首张唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/billie-eilish-album-review-when-we-all-fall-asleep-where-do-we-go-2467653">当我们都睡着了，我们去哪里？</a> 》中的《我爱你》。 &#39;。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-hit-by-necklace-thrown-by-fan-while-performing-3822272">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 在表演时被粉丝扔出的项链击中的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
